<div class="container">
    <div class="forgotpwd">
        <h3>找回密码</h3>
        <h5>So you forgot your password...</h5>
        <span></span>
        <p class="reset">Enter your email address in the box below, and we'll send you an Account Key . </p>
        <p>输入您的注册电子邮箱，我们会在发送一串验证码，已确定您的身份。并便于您重置密码。</p>
